230,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T00:52:21.000Z","msg":"雌蚊藉由特殊的感應器來尋找牠們的獵物。雌蚊對二氧化碳、熱及汗水非常敏感，所以牠們能在一定的距離內尋找恆溫動物的哺乳類和鳥叮咬。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"引咗佢離開你間房先， 再關門， 咁佢仲點咬你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"同你提過既見光完全無關係..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"好多scientists 話蚊係positive phototaxis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  &quot;完全無關&quot;?"},{"pid":"e9cacc79c425c2f677d9955f6b5a650083809e94","tid":591230,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"Lighted traps caught more mosquitoes than unlighted traps although the latter caught substantial numbers of Culex but not Aedes mosquitoes.<br />\n<br />\nThe light intensity of the bulb illuminating a trap was directly related to the numbers of individuals of a species taken by that trap, except in the case of C. p. quinquefasciatus females. In fact the number of mosquitoes appeared to be directly proportional to the light intensity, with the exception noted. No repellency was noted at the highest intensities tested."},{"pid":"bc3e4fab2fd46d133f4b430d65b88ac68ab4f255","tid":591230,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:10:28.000Z","msg":"biokill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e5527d1f1d1a79b0cda609350b012cb4f40d40","tid":591230,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"我用雷達電蚊香，開左冇煩惱"},{"pid":"3116b087981abe2cf9c0be2b316caa81754988f0","tid":591230,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e5527d1f1d1a79b0cda609350b012cb4f40d40","tid":591230,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"我用雷達電蚊香，開左冇煩惱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:24:44.000Z","msg":"試過唔太得，都係用殺蟲劑好啲，雖然唔健康"},{"pid":"