vents%2Fnih-research-matters%2Fhow-mosquitoes-detect-people&d=IhKlETWeGwy2SRW03p3ARtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c76f8fa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nih.gov/news-events/nih-research-matters/how-mosquitoes-detect-people</a><br />\n<br />\nResearchers discovered a receptor that mosquitoes use to detect both carbon dioxide and skin odor, and they identified compounds that interact with the receptor. The findings may help guide strategies to control mosquitoes and the diseases they transmit.<br />\n<br />\n囉2013既文出黎 我都覺得有D唔好意思"},{"pid":"2d3e9ab376f3f165b99baa2ef901a8fe49c0442e","tid":591230,"uid":35406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:22:06.000Z","msg":"之前係窗到貼蚊網 即刻冇蚊 但開窗好麻煩<br />\n依家買左個蚊帳 晚晚安心訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c41e5aa571d87be4eedb72ed1361254a9610099","tid":591230,"uid":45161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"電蚊香同蚊燈都試過唔work<br />\n最後都係點蚊香，但就會搞到成間房一陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f74580ce1bd0e4f69e2700686d1a028129cd9ed","tid":591230,"uid":119064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4106c93d70046eb39732cdbe104b3531bd85341","tid":591230,"uid":84148,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"認真答,貼蚊網係窗口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"貼左之後幾年未係屋企俾蚊咬過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc2c92180dfab11ac5cebcc1a912de4c579a9a7","tid":591230,"uid":90911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"用電蚊拍拍死晒佢"},{"pid":"407085fbbc2bcb5e51fecc7438baf558fb0a3435","tid":591230,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"蚊香"},{"pid":"3db1774a5e3317d92b4b7d43c8f6e1a66efac07a","tid":591230,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"其實你想證明咩野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你講既野同我講既有咩衝突? 你講carbon dioxide 令佢咬人， 無錯， 而我講緊蚊同其他昆蟲都有向光性， 熄燈會令佢減少入屋， 想問你問題係邊? 近年都有好多研究講咩顏色咩wavelength既light trap 會更有效捉蚊， 已經唔係講緊燈對蚊有無影響， 因為已經知有影響， 我同你講既野根本兩樣野， 無衝突， 點解你要否定燈會吸引蚊? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference: Field evaluation of three new mosquito light traps against two standard light traps to collect mosquitoes and non-target insects in northeast Florida (2015)"},{"pid":"e1940332c594d4f9719e47ca032c97bea5d42b55","tid":591230,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"揾個更易野蚊嘅人喺旁邊一齊訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係野蚊果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11160863dc2d89b4d2ab447b32d6fcdf05fad1dd","tid":591230,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"開冷氣<br />\n<br />\n萬試萬靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5682ea8c41086ba13ddb600335cae6aa00ba6a0c","tid":591230,"uid":70742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"956270f5c37b4207d9655555a6d8cf8bb5ae9f0e","tid":591230,"uid":101976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68129edc7c2baba22e5ef75c5f7c57f013f711f","tid":591230,"uid":89134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"打開蚊帳"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T11:28:46.000Z","msg